SPF Middle Tennesse Powerlifing Championship Results
Results for Middle Tennessee Powerlifting Championship 6/20/09 Cookeville Tn.

We want to thank everyone for coming out and being part of a great meet. We were expecting around 40 lifters or so and ended you with around 70 or better. Talk about lifters coming together. Also We want to take time to thank all the great people that really ran this meet for the SPF. Melissa Garrett, Josh Kylo,Victoria Rodgers, Wade Johnson, Rick Posey, and John Bible. Also thanks to all the loader/Spotters that worked on the platform ALL day. Especially thanks to Jacob Byrd, Frank Green and Donnie Millrany for all the help in setting up the meet and running it. It takes many people doing many things to pull off a great meet and when you can do it as easy as these people can that says a lot. Thanks to everyone from the spectators to the lifters and we will see you again real soon. Jesse Rodgers
